snippet.title: The Among Us Crewmate Joins Samurai Gunn 2!
snippet.description:
Play Samurai Gunn 2 now on Steam! https://store.steampowered.com/app/1397790/Samurai_Gunn_2/?utm_source=Youtube&utm_medium=description&utm_campaign=among-us-teaser
